"title": "4030: world, human behaviour in",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4030: world, human behaviour in",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Human behaviour in the world is now characterised by self-centredness as a result of sin. Believers are called upon to renounce such sinful behaviour.</p>\n<h2>Human passion in the world is expressed in various ways</h2>\n<h3>In physical desires</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:15-1John2:16\">1JN 2:15–2:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:17\">EXO 20:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov27:20\">PRO 27:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:15\">LUK 12:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:34\">LUK 21:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:4\">JAS 4:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:18-2Pet2:20\">2PE 2:18–2:20</a></p>\n<h3>In indulgence</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:1\">JAS 5:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:5\">JAS 5:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job21:7-Job21:13\">JOB 21:7–21:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps73:2-Ps73:3\">PSA 73:2–73:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:10\">2TI 4:10</a></p>\n<h3>In intellectual pursuits</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:8\">COL 2:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:3-Gal4:5\">GAL 4:3–4:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:3\">EPH 2:3</a></p>\n<h3>In a weak will</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:2\">EXO 23:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job31:34\">JOB 31:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:17-Rom6:19\">ROM 6:17–6:19</a></p>\n<h2>Though remaining in the world, believers are not of the world</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:6-John17:19\">JHN 17:6–17:19</a></p>\n<h2>Believers are to renounce the passions of the world</h2>\n<h3>Through a renewed mind</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:2\">ROM 12:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal1:4\">GAL 1:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:23\">EPH 4:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:5-Col3:10\">COL 3:5–3:10</a></p>\n<h3>Through obedience</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:14-1Pet1:15\">1PE 1:14–1:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor10:2-2Cor10:5\">2CO 10:2–10:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:24\">GAL 5:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:15\">GAL 6:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:17\">EPH 5:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:12\">TIT 2:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:27\">JAS 1:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:4\">2PE 1:4</a></p>\n<h3>Through having spiritual priorities</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:29-Luke12:31\">LUK 12:29–12:31</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:31-Matt6:33\">MAT 6:31–6:33</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:39\">MAT 10:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:26-Luke14:27\">LUK 14:26–14:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:33\">LUK 17:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:24-John12:26\">JHN 12:24–12:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:6\">1TI 6:6</a></p>\n<h3>Through growing to maturity</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:1\">1CO 3:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb5:12\">HEB 5:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:1-Heb6:3\">HEB 6:1–6:3</a></p>\n<h2>The futility of worldly pursuits</h2>\n<h3>They bring no lasting material gain</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:7\">1TI 6:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:21\">JOB 1:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps49:17\">PSA 49:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl5:15\">ECC 5:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:17-1Tim6:19\">1TI 6:17–6:19</a></p>\n<h3>They bring no spiritual gain</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:36-Mark8:37\">MRK 8:36–8:37</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:25\">LUK 9:25</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job20:4-Job20:5\">JOB 20:4–20:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps17:14\">PSA 17:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:25-Luke16:26\">LUK 16:25–16:26</a></p>",
